				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Once thing is that you do the hit detection wrong. I'm pretty should first wait the flag to be clear, then set (and you do the other way arround). That is because the flag is clear at the end of VBlank, and that your NMI code finish before that, so you wait the flag to be clear. And then you wait the flag to be set again, when set sprite zero hit occured. And wait for the flag to be clear wait the end of the VBlank, it don't have anything to do with HBlank.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

