				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">When you change the horizontal scroll via $2005, bits 0-2 take effect immediately, while bits 3-7 don't take effect until H-Blank.  When writing to $2000, bit 0 (horizontal nametable) takes effect at H-Blank.
<br />
<br />To avoid glitching at the right side of the screen, make sure the second nametable is filled with transparent tiles in the area covered by the status bar.
<br />
<br />BTW, your sprite 0 code can be optimized if you use BIT:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">WaitClear:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bit $2002<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bvs WaitClear<br />WaitSet:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bit $2002<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bvc WaitSet</div></div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />"Last version was better," says Floyd. "More bugs. Bugs make game fun."</div>
					<br clear="all" /><br />

