					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I'm thinking that your response is for a status bar at the bottom of the screen.   I should have mentioned mine is at the top of the screen.
<br />
<br />Here's a pic of the glitch.  The black at the bottom right of the status area varies in width as I scroll. Anywhere from 0 to 6 pixels in width.
<br />
