					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Wizards and Warriors 3 uses a single pixel.  In fact, it does some crazy and neat tricks to ensure that there will always be a pixel in the location where it collides.  I'm sure rare wouldn't have done it that way if a single pixel didn't work.
<br />
<br />Note #3 basically means that it clears the hitflag on scanline #0.  (otherwise it would stay on all the time)</div>

					
